title: AIIMS Jammu Recruitment 2025 - Apply Online for Project Technical Support Post
description: All India Institute of Medical Science Jammu (AIIMS Jammu) has declared the official notification for 2025. To fill up the vacancies for Project Technical Support Jobs. Those candidates who have qualified in the Diploma, DMLT, and B.Sc can grab this chance and apply for the AIIMS Jammu Recruitment 2025 .
